<item>
            <title>[LU-18111] Don&apos;t drop expired cancel request</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18111</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;   There is no need to drop expired cancel request by&lt;br/&gt;
    a server because the client will resend the same content.&lt;br/&gt;
    Even if the server is heavy loaded cancel request processing&lt;br/&gt;
    helps to release ldlm resources and avoids spending time&lt;br/&gt;
    on processing of the same resends.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
